React.ReactElement<any,string|React.JSXE.description:
Represents a JSX element.

Where {@link ReactNode} represents everything that can be rendered, `ReactElement`
only represents JSX.

props.description: The type of the props object

type.description: The type of the component or tag

React.ReactNode.description:
Represents all of the things React can render.

Where {@link ReactElement} only represents JSX, `ReactNode` represents everything that can be rendered.

props.description: The type of the props object

type.description: The type of the component or tag

base.description: Set base classes for the root element.

classes.description: Provide arbitrary classes to the root element.

controlActive.description: Set active state classes for the control element.

controlBase.description: Set base classes for the control element.

controlClasses.description: Provide arbitrary classes to the control element.

controlDisabled.description: Set disabled state classes for the control element.

controlHeight.description: Set height classes for the control element.

controlHover.description: Set hover classes for the control element.

controlInactive.description: Set inactive state classes for the control element.

controlPadding.description: Set padding classes for the control element.

controlRounded.description: Set rounded classes for the control element.

controlWidth.description: Set width classes for the control element.

form.description: The id of the form that the switch belongs to

getRootNode.description: A root node to correctly resolve document in custom environments. E.x.: Iframes, Electron.

iconActiveBase.description: Set base classes for the active icon child.

iconInactiveBase.description: Set base classes for the inactive icon child.

ids.description: The ids of the elements in the switch. Useful for composition.

invalid.description: If `true`, the switch is marked as invalid.

label.description: Specifies the localized strings that identifies the accessibility elements and their states

labelBase.description: Set base classes for the label element.

labelClasses.description: Provide arbitrary classes to the label element.

name.description: Set a unique name for the switch input.

onCheckedChange.description: Triggers when the switch is toggled.

required.description: If `true`, the switch input is marked as required,

stateFocused.description: Set claseses for the focus state.

thumbActive.description: Set active classes for the thumb element.

thumbBase.description: Set base classes for the thumb element.

thumbClasses.description: Provide arbitrary classes to the thumb element.

thumbDuration.description: Set animation duration classes for the thumb element.

thumbEase.description: Set animation easing classes for the thumb element.

thumbInactive.description: Set inactive classes for the thumb element.

thumbRounded.description: Set rounded classes for the thumb element.

thumbTransition.description: Set animation transition classes for the thumb element.

thumbTranslateX.description: Set animation X-axis translate classes for the thumb element.

value.description: The value of switch input. Useful for form submission.
